993
01:44:06,580 --> 01:44:08,420
They would just ignore and go and sing in it.

994
01:44:08,420 --> 01:44:09,420
So what are you going to do?

995
01:44:09,420 --> 01:44:10,420
You know, electrocuted them.

996
01:44:10,420 --> 01:44:12,700
Just be going to sing.

997
01:44:12,700 --> 01:44:18,580
So my older two children wanted to go to jail.

998
01:44:18,580 --> 01:44:20,340
My wife was in jail.

999
01:44:20,340 --> 01:44:23,100
I was sleeping in different places every night and I just couldn't handle that.

1000
01:44:23,100 --> 01:44:24,820
That was too much.

1001
01:44:24,820 --> 01:44:30,260
That's when John and Richard Dean chat well said, we'll take care of the kids.

1002
01:44:30,260 --> 01:44:32,300
They wanted to be a part of it.

1003
01:44:32,300 --> 01:44:37,660
Now, they have been back to Albany this year.

1004
01:44:37,660 --> 01:44:43,180
They take tremendous pride in the Albany Civil Rights Institute because they say the

1005
01:44:43,180 --> 01:44:48,500
first thing we see when we walk in there is the quote from my father.

1006
01:44:48,500 --> 01:44:54,820
Any final thoughts?

1007
01:44:54,820 --> 01:44:55,820
I produce it.

1008
01:44:55,820 --> 01:44:57,980
I say I produce it.

1009
01:44:57,980 --> 01:45:04,340
I am the one who organizes this visiting minority faculty series at Michigan State

1010
01:45:04,340 --> 01:45:05,340
University.

1011
01:45:06,340 --> 01:45:10,060
It's been going on for 12 years.

1012
01:45:10,060 --> 01:45:16,380
During the month of February, black history month, every Thursday I bring in a distinguished

1013
01:45:16,380 --> 01:45:22,540
primarily African American scholars from civil rights era, primarily.

1014
01:45:22,540 --> 01:45:26,980
Some are brought in who are not African American like Tom Hayden and some that are more

1015
01:45:26,980 --> 01:45:34,340
contemporary like Charles Adams and who else have had contemporary.

1016
01:45:34,340 --> 01:45:44,080
But anyway, I was brought in the boy from down in Georgia that was there with Nick

1017
01:45:44,080 --> 01:45:45,580
Charles-Sharad.

1018
01:45:45,580 --> 01:45:50,660
She had a little bit of controversy that she got into with the President of the administration.

1019
01:45:50,660 --> 01:45:58,940
I brought her up there because she symbolizes the resistance that we had when people were

1020
01:45:58,940 --> 01:45:59,940
not being treated right.

1021
01:45:59,940 --> 01:46:04,940
In other words, she was doing the right thing and somehow another she got characterizes

1022
01:46:04,940 --> 01:46:10,140
or she was characterizes doing the wrong thing against white folks.

1023
01:46:10,140 --> 01:46:12,140
Anyway, I brought her up.

1024
01:46:12,140 --> 01:46:17,540
I am very proud of the fact that I have been able to bring them for 12 years now distinguished

1025
01:46:17,540 --> 01:46:24,580
African American scholars starting with my friend in New York, Wyatt T. Walker, who was

1026
01:46:24,580 --> 01:46:26,780
just outstanding.

1027
01:46:26,860 --> 01:46:31,300
I brought people like Juanita Ebenethi.

1028
01:46:31,300 --> 01:46:35,300
All she had to do was just tell the story how she lived at her house was barmed.

1029
01:46:35,300 --> 01:46:41,500
Now, her husband's property was taken away and now he died ignominiously.

1030
01:46:41,500 --> 01:46:46,380
And I brought up people like Joe Lowry, who was the, if you were the grandfather of the

1031
01:46:46,380 --> 01:46:47,380
movement.

1032
01:46:47,380 --> 01:46:50,340
I brought Bernie Stranson up twice.

1033
01:46:50,340 --> 01:46:52,740
I brought Duret the cotton.

1034
01:46:52,740 --> 01:46:55,740
These are the people that made the history.

1035
01:46:55,740 --> 01:47:01,100
And what I have said to myself and others in Michigan State is it's one thing to read

1036
01:47:01,100 --> 01:47:02,580
about it.

1037
01:47:02,580 --> 01:47:07,860
It's another thing to actually talk to the people who lived it.

1038
01:47:07,860 --> 01:47:12,940
It's sort of like the parallel I draw about Jesus Christ who came down off the cross and

1039
01:47:12,940 --> 01:47:20,220
there was doubt and Thomas put your finger in the womb where the spear was.

1040
01:47:20,220 --> 01:47:24,980
And I tell these people, Michigan State, come and talk to the people that went to jail,

1041
01:47:24,980 --> 01:47:31,220
