1042
01:47:31,220 --> 01:47:32,540
These were real people.

1043
01:47:32,540 --> 01:47:34,660
This is not fiction.

1044
01:47:34,660 --> 01:47:37,420
These were real people.

1045
01:47:37,420 --> 01:47:41,420
I'm very grateful and it's a real honor and a privilege.

1046
01:47:41,420 --> 01:47:42,420
Your own time.

1047
